c: 11
v: 27
t: "Akuluakulu osakhulupirira amene adali pakati pa anthu ake adati: “Ife tili kukuona iwe ngati munthu onga ife tomwe ndiponso tili kuona kuti onse amene ali kukutsatira kuti ndi anthu apansi kwambiri pakati pathu ndiponso iwo akutsatira iwe osaganiza. Ndipo ife sitili kuona china chilichonse mwa iwe chopambana ife ndipo, kunena moona, tikuganiza kuti inu ndinu abodza.”"